'''अन्तरङ्ग''' a highly technical term in āṇini's grammar applied in a ariety of ways to rules which hereby can supersede other ules. The term is not used y Pāṇini himself. The Vārti- akāra has used the term thrice  Sec I. 4. 2 Vārt. 8, VI.1.106 art.10 and VIII.2.6 Vārt. I) vidently in the sense of imme-



