 f several operations which take
 lace in arriving at the complete orm of a word, (5) not having संज्ञा technical term) as a cause of its pplication, ( 6 ) not depending pon two words or padas, (7) de- ending upon a cause or causes of a eneral nature (सामान्यापेक्ष) as oppos- d to one which depends on causes f a specific nature ( विशेषापेक्ष).

'''अन्तरङ्गपरिभाषा''' the phrase is used enerally for the परिभाषा "असिद्धं बहि- ङ्गमन्तरङ्गे' described above. See the ord अन्तरङ्ग. The परिभाषा has got a ery wide field of application and s used several times in setting side difficulties which present hemselves in the formation of a ord. Like many other paribhāṣās his paribhāṣā is not a paribhāṣā f universal application.

