'asiddham , bahiraṅgam anta- aṅga' Par. Śek. Pari. 50 and the iscussion thereon. Some gram- arians have given the name सिद्धपरिभाषा to the Paribhāṣā असिद्धं हिरङ्गमन्तरङ्गे as contrasted with न्तरङ्गं बहुिरङ्कगाद् वलीयः which they ave named as बहिरङ्गपरिभाषा.

