'''अस्पष्ट''' less in contact with the vocal rgan than the semi-vowels; the erm occurs in Hemacandra's rammar (Hem. I.3.25) and is xplained by the commentator s 'ईषत्स्पृष्टतरौ प्रत्यासत्तेर्यकारवकारौ. अस्पष्ट tands for the letters य and च which re substituted for the vowels ए  and ओ औ when followed by a owel; cf, also Śāk I.I.154.

