'''अपिशालि''' an ancient grammarian entioned by Pāṇini and his ommentators like Patañjali, Hela- āja and others; cf. वा सुप्यापिशलेः P. V.3.98; तथा चापिशलेर्विधिः M. Bh. n IV.2.45.

'''आपुक्''' augment आप् added to the ords सत्य, अर्थ and वेद् before the ffix णिच्; cf. M. Bh. on III.1.25  nd Vārt. l and 2 thereon; e.g. त्यापयति, अर्थापयति, वदापयति.

