 he grammars of Jainendra, Śāka- āyana, Cāndra and Hemacandra; f. Cāndra II I. 43; Jainendra I. .119; Śāk.IV.3.120: Hem. II.3.31. Hence, the term साप्य s used for a transitive root in hese grammars.

