'''अास्तारपङ्कति''' a variety of पङ्कक्ति metre f 40 letters with 8 letters in the irst and second quarters or pādas nd 12 letters in the third and ourth quarters cf. अास्तारपङ्कक्तिरा- ितः R.Pr.XVI.40. For instances f आस्तारपङ्क्ति see Ṛgveda sūkta 2l, andala X.

