'''आस्वदीय''' a sub-division of the चुरादि Xth conj.) roots, beginning with he root ग्रस् and ending with the oot स्वद्, which take the Vikaraṇa िच् i.e. which are conjugated like oots of the tenth conjugation, nly if they are transitive in ense.

'''अाहञ्''' tad-affix (आह) in the general aiṣika senses, e.g. belonging to, roduced in, etc., added to the ord उत्तर, e.g. औत्तराह cf. उत्तरादाहञ् क्तव्यः।; M.Bh. on IV.2.104.

