'''इञ्''' (l) kṛt. affix (इ), in the sense of erbal activity applied to any root, he word so formed being used in he fem. gender and in connection ith narration or in interrogation; .g. कां त्वं कारिमकार्षी । सर्वौ कारिमकार्षम् । f. Pāṇini III.3.110: (2) kṛt. affix n the sense of verbal activity pplied to the roots वप् and others .g. वापिः, वासि: etc. cf. P.III.3.108 ārt. 7;(3) tad-affix इ in the sense f offspring applied to a noun nding in अ; e.g, दाक्षि: cf. P.IV.1. 5-7, 153.

